<title>USA: Cadence Design Q1 shr rises.</title>
<headline>Cadence Design Q1 shr rises.</headline>
<dateline>SAN JOSE, Calif. 1997-04-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>Cadence Design Systems, Inc.</p>
<p>		  Condensed Consolidated Statements of Income</p>
<p>For the Quarters Ended March 29, 1997 and March 30, 1996</p>
<p>			(in 000's, except per share amounts)</p>
<p>				     (Unaudited)</p>
<p>					Mar 29,		     Mar 30,</p>
<p>					  1997			   1996</p>
<p> PRODUCT REVENUE		 $102,323		     $90,182</p>
<p> SERVICES REVENUE		  33,753			23,098</p>
